00726 inline double MAnalyzer::makeSubRanking( int i, Eojul& eojul )
00727 {
00728         double value = 0.0;
00729         int j, cnt = eojul.getCount(i);
00730 
00731         for( j = 0; j < cnt; j++ )
00732         {
00733                 char* pLexicon = eojul.getLexicon( i, j );
00734                 int POS        = eojul.getPOS( i, j );
00735 
00736                 if( POS & N_ )
00737                 {
00738                         if( POS & NNg )
00739                         {
00740                                 value += SCORE_NNG * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00741 
00742                                 if( (int)strlen( eojul.getBufferPtr() ) == 6 )
00743                                 {
00744                                         value -= 0.1;
00745                                 }
00746                         }
00747 
00748                         if( POS & NNf )
00749                         {
00750                                 value += SCORE_NNF * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00751                         }
00752 
00753                         if( POS & NNi )
00754                         {
00755                                 value += SCORE_NNI * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00756                         }
00757 
00758                         if( POS & Np )
00759                         {
00760                                 value += SCORE_NP * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00761                         }
00762 
00763                         if( POS & Nu )
00764                         {
00765                                 value += SCORE_NU * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00766                         }
00767 
00768                         if( POS & NNu )
00769                         {
00770                                 value += SCORE_NNU * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE ) ;
00771                         }
00772 
00773                         if( POS & NNb )
00774                         {
00775                                 value += SCORE_NNB * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00776 
00777                                 if( (j > 0) && ( eojul.getPOS( i, j-1 ) & SN ) )
00778                                 {
00779                                         value += 0.7;
00780                                 }
00781                         }
00782                 }
00783                 if( POS & IC )
00784                 {
00785                         value += SCORE_IC * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00786                 }
00787 
00788                 if( POS & MA )
00789                 {
00790                         value += SCORE_MA * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00791                 }
00792 
00793                 if( POS & MM )
00794                 {
00795                         value += SCORE_MM * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00796                 }
00797 
00798                 if( POS & V_ )
00799                 {
00800                         if( POS & Vv )
00801                         {
00802                                 value += SCORE_VV * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00803                                 if( _flagV_ == 3 )      value += 1.0;
00804                                 _flagV_ = 1;
00805                         }
00806 
00807                         if( POS & Va )
00808                         {
00809                                 value += SCORE_VA * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00810                                 if( _flagV_ == 3 )      value += 1.0;
00811                                 _flagV_ = 2;
00812                         }
00813                 }
00814 
00815                 if( POS & VX )
00816                 {
00817                         value += SCORE_VX * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00818                 }
00819 
00820                 if( (POS & XSD) && (_flagV_ == 0) )
00821                 {
00822                         if( strlen( eojul.getBufferPtr() ) >= 8 )
00823                         {
00824                                 value += 0.67;
00825                         }
00826                         else
00827                         {
00828                                 value += 0.47;
00829                         }
00830 
00831                         if( strcmp( pLexicon, "하" ) == 0 )
00832                         {
00833                                 value += 0.18;
00834                         }
00835 
00836                         _flagV_ = 3;
00837                 }
00838 
00839                 if( (POS & J_) )
00840                 {
00841                         size_t len = strlen( pLexicon );
00842 
00843                         if( len <= 2 )      value += 0.1;
00844                         else if( len <= 4 ) value += 0.3;
00845                         else if( len > 4  ) value += 0.25 * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00846                 }
00847 
00848                 if( (POS & E_) )
00849                 {
00850                         size_t len = strlen( pLexicon );
00851 
00852                         if( len <= 2 )      value += 0.1;
00853                         else if( len <= 4 ) value += 0.3;
00854                         else if( len > 4  ) value += 0.25 * ( strlen( pLexicon ) * SCORE_LEN_VALUE );
00855                 }
00856 
00857                 if( (POS & VC) )
00858                 {
00859                         value -= 0.37;
00860                 }
00861 
00862                 if( (POS & EP) == EP )
00863                 {
00864                         value -= 0.37;
00865                 }
00866         }
00867 
00868         if( value < 0 ) return value * (-1);
00869         
00870         return value;
00871 }
00872 
00873 int MAnalyzer::makeRanking( Eojul& eojul )
00874 {
00875         int sizeList = eojul.getListSize();
00876 
00877         if( sizeList < 1 ) return 0;
00878 
00879         if( sizeList == 1 )
00880         {
00881                 if( isPerformedNNR && ( *( eojul.getScoresPtr() + 1 ) > 0 ) ) return 1;
00882 
00883                 *(eojul.getScoresPtr() + 1 ) = 1;
00884 
00885                 return 1;
00886         }
00887 
00888         int i;
00889         _flagV_ = 0;
00890         
00891         for( i = 0; i < sizeList; i++ )
00892         {
00893                 if( *( eojul.getScoresPtr() + i + 1 ) <= 0 )
00894                 {
00895                         *( eojul.getScoresPtr() + i + 1 ) = makeSubRanking( i, eojul );
00896                         if( isPerformedNNR == true )
00897                         {
00898                                 *( eojul.getScoresPtr() + i + 1 ) *= 0.87;
00899                         }
00900                 }
00901         }
00902 
00903         return 1;
00904 }

01021 int MAnalyzer::analyzeSubHangulWordforSN( Eojul& eojul, const StringEx& hangul )
01022 {
01023         int ret = -1;
01024         int tag = 0, N_tag = 0;
01025         int hangulLength = (int)hangul.length();
01026 
01027         SearchInfo si;
01028         _dic->searchNgetInfoFromMainTrie( hangul, si, hangulLength );
01029         tag   = si.mti.tag;
01030         N_tag = tag;
01031 
01032         if( eojul.getCount( eojul.getListSize()-1 ) == 0 )
01033         {
01034                 if( tag & MM )
01035                 {
01036                         eojul.setMorphAndTag( hangul.buffer(), MM );
01037                         ret = 1;
01038                         return 1;
01039                 }
01040                 else if( tag & MA )
01041                 {
01042                         eojul.setMorphAndTag( hangul.buffer(), MA );
01043                         ret = 1;
01044                         return 1;
01045                 }
01046                 else if( tag & NNg )
01047                 {
01048                         int tagNNF = si.mti.isNNF ? NNF : NNG;
01049 
01050                         eojul.setMorphAndTag( hangul.buffer(), tagNNF );
01051                         ret = 1;
01052                         return 1;
01053                 }
01054         }
01055 
01056         if( tag & NNb )
01057         {               
01058                 if( eojul.getCountsPtr()[0] > 1 )
01059                 {                                               
01060                         Eojul peojul;
01061                         peojul.setEojulAndInfo( hangul.buffer(), EI_HANGUL );
01062                         peojul.increaseAnalysisResults();
01063                         peojul.setMorphAndTag ( hangul.buffer(), NNB );
01064                         peojul.close();
01065 
01066                         eojul.close();
01067                         Eojul tmpEojul = eojul;
01068                         eojul.initialize();
01069                         eojul.setEojulAndInfo( tmpEojul.getBufferPtr(), tmpEojul.getEojulInfo() );
01070                         eojul.merge( tmpEojul, peojul );
01071                 }
01072                 else    eojul.setMorphAndTag( hangul.buffer(), NNB );
01073 
01074                 ret = 1;
01075                 return 1;
01076         }
01077         else
01078         {               
01079                 SearchJEInfo sjei;
01080                 _dic->searchNgetInfoFromJosaEomiTrie( hangul, sjei, hangulLength );
01081                 tag = sjei.jeti.tag;
01082 
01083                 if( (tag & J_) && (sjei.pos == hangulLength) && (sjei.posEnd == 0) && ((hangulLength == 2) || !(N_tag & N_)) )
01084                 {
01085                         if( eojul.getCountsPtr()[0] > 1 )
01086                         {                                               
01087                                 Eojul peojul;
01088                                 peojul.setEojulAndInfo( hangul.buffer(), EI_HANGUL );
01089                                 peojul.increaseAnalysisResults();
01090                                 peojul.setMorphAndTag ( hangul.buffer(), J_ );
01091                                 peojul.close();
01092 
01093                                 eojul.close();
01094                                 Eojul tmpEojul = eojul;
01095                                 eojul.initialize();
01096                                 eojul.setEojulAndInfo( tmpEojul.getBufferPtr(), tmpEojul.getEojulInfo() );
01097                                 eojul.merge( tmpEojul, peojul );
01098                         }
01099                         else    eojul.setMorphAndTag( hangul.buffer(), J_ );
01100 
01101                         return 1;
01102                 }
01103         }
01104 
01105         int yurFlag = 0;
01106         int vcFlag = 0;

04269 int MAnalyzer::analyzeHeadTail( Eojul& eojul, SearchJEInfo& sjei )
04270 {
04271         int retCode = CODE_FAIL;
04272 
04273         int flagNJ = 1;
04274 
04275         SyllableInfo* psi;
04276 
04277         memset( &_jeInfo,  0x0, sizeof(JEInfo) );
04278         memset( &_jecInfo, 0x0, sizeof(JEInfo) );
04279 
04280         _infoHT[_depthHT].strHead.setSubString( eojul.getBufferPtr(), sjei.pos );
04281 
04282         if( sjei.jeti.tag & J_ )
04283         {
04284                 _jeInfo = _dic->getJEInfo( sjei, 0 );
04285         }
04286 
04287         if( _jeInfo.pstr != 0 && (_jeInfo.tag & J_) )
04288         {
04289                 psi = ExCP949::getInfoEnd( _infoHT[_depthHT].strHead.buffer() );
04290                 if( psi == 0 ) return ( retCode | CODE_ERROR );
04291 
04292                 JEInfo jeInfo = _jeInfo;
04293 
04294                 _infoHT[_depthHT].strTail = _jeInfo.pstr;
04295                 _infoHT[_depthHT].strTail += eojul.getBufferPtr() + _posTail;
04296                 _infoHT[_depthHT].tagTail = _jeInfo.tag;
04297 
04298                 if( !(eojul.getEojulInfo() & EI_AUXVERB) )
04299                 {
04300                         if( _jeInfo.info & JDI_ONLY_NP )
04301                         {
04302                                 if( (flagNJ = canBeNJ( psi, _jeInfo )) && checkNanalyzeN_( eojul, NP ) & CODE_SUCCESS ) retCode |= CODE_SUCCESS;
04303                         }
04304                         else
04305                         {
04306                                 if( (flagNJ = canBeNJ( psi, _jeInfo )) && checkNanalyzeN_( eojul, (NNG | NNB | NNP | NNU | NP | NU | NNI | MA) ) & CODE_SUCCESS )
04307                                 {
04308                                         retCode                  |= CODE_SUCCESS;
04309                                         _historyAnalysis |= J_;
04310                                 }
04311                         }
04312                 }
04313 
04314                 if( !(_jeInfo.info & JDI_ONLY_N_) && (psi->coda == hlM || (!(psi->info & CODA) && (psi->onset == hfG) && (psi->nucleus == hmEE))) )
04315                 {
04316                         int len = (int)_infoHT[_depthHT].strHead.length();
04317 
04318                         if( psi->coda == hlM && !(psi->onset == hfO && psi->nucleus == hmUH) )

04320                                 _infoHT[_depthHT+1].strHead = _infoHT[_depthHT].strHead;
04321 
04322                                 _depthHT++;
04323 
04324                                 if( analyzeSimpleWord( eojul ) & CODE_SUCCESS )
04325                                 {
04326                                         retCode |= CODE_SUCCESS;
04327                                         _nnrJ = 1;
04328                                 }
04329 
04330                                 _depthHT--;
04331                         }
04332                         else

04341

04367                         {
04368                                 if( checkNanalyzeContraction_KEE( eojul ) & CODE_SUCCESS ) retCode |= CODE_SUCCESS;

04371

04373                         && (_posTail == (int)strlen( eojul.getBufferPtr())) && ((_historyAnalysis & EP_SS) != EP_SS) 
04374                         && ((_jeInfo.info & JDI_ONLY_NP) != JDI_ONLY_NP) )

04386                 _infoHT[_depthHT].tagTail = _jeInfo.tag;
04387 
04388                 if( analyzeDeclinableWord( eojul, sjei ) & CODE_SUCCESS )
04389                 {
04390                         retCode |= CODE_SUCCESS;
04391                 }
04392         }
04393

05942         {
05943                 _avEojul.initialize();

05952

05965                                 }
05966                                 else if( _avEojul.getPOS( a, _avEojul.getCount( a )-1 ) & J_ )
05967                                 {
05968                                         flag = 2;

05971

05973                         {
05974                                 eojul.merge( _avEojul, _gcList._avList[i] );

05976                         else if( flag == 2 )
05977                         {
05978                                 _gcList._avList[i].getTagsPtr()[2] = V_;
05979                                 eojul.merge( _avEojul, _gcList._avList[i] );
05980                         }
05981                         else
05982                         {
05983                                 _isAnalyzed = 0;
05984                                 ret = 0;
05985                         }
05986 
05987                         break;
05988                 }
05989         }
